-- models/intermediate/int_deduped_channels.sql
```sql
-- Deduplicate customer_channels to primary attribution (earliest per customer)
WITH source AS (
    SELECT
        customer_id,
        channel,
        attributed_at,
        ROW_NUMBER() OVER (
            PARTITION BY customer_id
            ORDER BY attributed_at ASC
        ) AS row_num
    FROM {{ ref('stg_customer_channels') }}
)
SELECT
    customer_id,
    channel
FROM source
WHERE row_num = 1
```

-- models/intermediate/int_transactions_enriched.sql
```sql
-- Enrich transactions with store location and deduped channel attribution
WITH source AS (
    SELECT
        t.transaction_id,
        t.customer_id,
        t.amount,
        t.transaction_date,
        s.city,
        ch.channel
    FROM {{ ref('stg_transactions') }} t
    LEFT JOIN {{ ref('stg_stores') }} s
        ON s.store_id = t.store_id
    LEFT JOIN {{ ref('int_deduped_channels') }} ch
        ON ch.customer_id = t.customer_id
)
SELECT * FROM source
```

-- models/marts/fct_revenue_by_channel_city.sql
```sql
-- Customer revenue by attribution channel and store city
WITH source AS (
    SELECT
        COALESCE(t.channel, '(unknown)') AS channel,
        COALESCE(t.city, '(unknown)') AS city,
        SUM(t.amount) AS total_revenue,
        COUNT(*) AS transaction_count,
        COUNT(DISTINCT t.customer_id) AS unique_customers
    FROM {{ ref('int_transactions_enriched') }} t
    GROUP BY
        COALESCE(t.channel, '(unknown)'),
        COALESCE(t.city, '(unknown)')
)
SELECT * FROM source
